race.comment: NAZWAH (11) above average filly resuming. Lived up to expectations on debut when a sharp winner over 1100m at Gosford. Sent straight to the paddock when sixth over 1100m at Randwick last July. Impressed in her two trials and will take catching today. STRAAND BEAUTY (4) stalked the speed second-up and turned in a gritty effort with the 59kg when a narrow third over this track and trip. Can take the sit here and close late. SHALAA GOLD (2) consistent sprinter resuming on his home track. Raced well in this company last prep and looks ready to go after the two slick trials. Go close from the inside gate. GENEROUS HARRY (3) has returned in terrific form and is going too good to ignore.
